---
import ContentLayout from '../layouts/ContentLayout.astro';
---

<ContentLayout
  title="Disclaimer"
  description="Legal disclaimer for Own Your Mind — not financial advice."
  breadcrumbs={[{ label: 'Disclaimer' }]}
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Disclaimer</h1>

    <div class="prose">
      <p class="text-lg text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">
        Own Your Mind is an independent content platform. We write about decentralised AI from a practitioner perspective.
        What follows is the boring-but-important bit about what this site is and isn't.
      </p>

      <h2>Not Financial Advice</h2>

      <p>
        Nothing on this site — including project reviews, Freedom Scores, Returns Scores, tokenomics analysis,
        or any other content — constitutes financial, investment, legal, or tax advice. It is published for
        informational and educational purposes only.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>Do not make investment decisions based on what you read here.</strong> Our scores reflect our
        independent assessment at the time of writing. They are opinions, not recommendations. Always do your
        own research and consult a qualified professional before making financial decisions.
      </p>

      <h2>Cryptocurrency Risk Warning</h2>

      <p>
        Cryptocurrency and digital assets are high-risk. You should not invest unless you are prepared to lose
        all of the money you invest. This is not a protected investment — if something goes wrong, you should not
        expect to be made whole.
      </p>

      <p>Specific risks include but are not limited to:</p>

      <ul>
        <li>Extreme price volatility</li>
        <li>Total loss of value</li>
        <li>Regulatory changes that may affect legality, access, or value</li>
        <li>Smart contract failures, exploits, or rug pulls</li>
        <li>Projects ceasing operations without notice</li>
        <li>Illiquidity — you may not be able to sell when you want to</li>
      </ul>

      <p>Past performance is not indicative of future results.</p>

      <h2>Accuracy and Completeness</h2>

      <p>
        We do our best to be accurate, but we make no guarantees. Information on this site may contain errors,
        may be incomplete, or may become outdated. The crypto space moves fast — a review written last month
        may not reflect today's reality.
      </p>

      <p>
        We are not liable for any losses, damages, or costs arising from your use of this site or reliance on
        its content.
      </p>

      <h2>Independence</h2>

      <p>
        All opinions are our own. We are not sponsored by, affiliated with, or compensated by any project
        reviewed on this site. We hold positions in some of the tokens we write about — when relevant, we
        disclose this in the article. If our independence status changes, we will update this section.
      </p>

      <h2>Not an Offer or Solicitation</h2>

      <p>
        Nothing on this site constitutes an offer, solicitation, or recommendation to buy, sell, or hold any
        cryptocurrency, token, or digital asset.
      </p>

      <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-tertiary)] mt-8">
        Last updated: March 2026
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</ContentLayout>
